		<Component name="N1733216559530_1" type="note" x="499" y="62" w="300" h="112" title="Collect all users :&#xA;- Join DSUsers with Vault_Users to get the user type (EPVUser)&#xA;- Join with Users to get the usertype and the lastlogindate"/>
